```catala-metadata
declaration scope S:
  input x content integer
  input y content boolean
  input z content money

  output r content money

scope S:
  definition r equals if x > 0 and y then z else $0
```

```catala-test-cli
$ catala test-scope S --json-input {"x":1,"y":true,"z":123}
┌─[RESULT]─ S ─
│ r = $123.00
└─
```

